1
00:00:18,766 --> 00:00:22,446
CJ Foods US, Twin Cities Campus
is embarking on a new journey

2
00:00:22,447 --> 00:00:23,586
of challenge and change.

3
00:00:23,587 --> 00:00:25,459
Here is the story of a special moment

4
00:00:25,459 --> 00:00:27,871
of aligning on the goals and tasks for growth,

5
00:00:27,872 --> 00:00:30,097
and a future vision to be achieved as one team.

6
00:00:45,412 --> 00:00:50,644
With CJ Foods US, TCC’s
new and core products on display,

7
00:00:50,645 --> 00:00:52,986
K-flavor innovations are introduced.

8
00:01:00,834 --> 00:01:03,028
And the cooking process of a new pizza,

9
00:01:03,029 --> 00:01:05,899
showcasing differentiated technology,
is demonstrated.

10
00:01:11,437 --> 00:01:14,297
The Chairman and the employees
sample the products

11
00:01:14,298 --> 00:01:16,178
and engage in lively discussions

12
00:01:16,179 --> 00:01:18,645
on strategies to make each one
more competitive.

13
00:01:36,122 --> 00:01:38,109
After exchanging diverse views,

14
00:01:38,110 --> 00:01:41,568
Chairman Lee Jay Hyun
stressed the importance of product innovation

15
00:01:41,568 --> 00:01:44,906
and differentiated competitiveness
driven by ONLYONE.

16
00:02:23,183 --> 00:02:25,112
In the round table meeting with leaders,

17
00:02:25,112 --> 00:02:27,743
there was open dialogue
and shared understanding

18
00:02:27,744 --> 00:02:30,384
on leadership, innovation, synergy,

19
00:02:30,384 --> 00:02:32,853
and the goals and vision to achieve
as one team.

20
00:04:00,974 --> 00:04:04,579
Closing his visit to CJ Foods US, TCC,

21
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:06,813
the Chairman presented gifts to the employees.

22
00:04:06,813 --> 00:04:08,219
He promised to return

23
00:04:08,220 --> 00:04:11,131
and reminded them
that by drawing on the ONLYONE spirit

24
00:04:11,132 --> 00:04:13,398
and taking bold initiatives together as one,

25
00:04:13,399 --> 00:04:15,088
they can accelerate growth.

